"ABBREVIATION_DAY":"d","ABBREVIATION_MONTH":"mo","ABOUT_INCLUDED":"about what\'s included.","ABOUT_INSIGHTS":"About insights","ABOUT_INSIGHTS_DESCRIPTION":"Get insights about tasks performed by your teams to help you organize and plan your projects. You can view insights based on aggregated user data at a team level and filter by teams or categories to consider what actions to take. At this time, only Premium plan customers are able to see user-level details. You can turn off user-detail view if you do not wish to see this data.","ABOUT_INSIGHTS_CONTENT":"Unlock the power of the products you use. Discover new features, commands, and workflows based on how you work and the work that you do.","ABOUT_TEAM_INSIGHTS":"About team insights","ABOUT_TEAM_INSIGHTS_CONTENT":"Team insights help inform administrative tasks to better organize teams. Filter by teams or categories to consider what actions to take.","ABOUT_PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_MSG":"For your convenience, Autodesk offers functions that let you review your and/or your personnel\'s Autodesk software usage information. By accessing this information, you acknowledge and agree that you are responsible for providing any notices and obtaining any consents required under any applicable state, local, national or other data privacy and employment laws and regulations, including, but not limited to, such laws and regulations promulgated by the European Union.","ACC_MODAL_TITLE":"Autodesk Constuction Cloud (ACC) products are now included in your usage reporting","ACC_MODAL_CONTENT":"Reporting is now available for the following products, with data captured as far back as October 10, 2023:","ACC_MODAL_FOOTER":"Data from Flex ACC users is not supported in usage reporting at this time.","ACCESS_OPTION":"Access option","ACCESS_OPTIONS":"Access options","ACTIVE":"Active","ACTIVE_USERS":"Active users","ACTIVE_USERS_TOOLTIP":"Users who are currently assigned to a product and used that product in the selected date range.","ADAPTIVE_BANNER":"More details are available when viewed on a larger screen.","ADJUSTMENTS":"Adjustments","ADJUSTMENT_DATE":"Adjustment date","ADJUSTMENT_TOOLTIP":"Positive values indicate token consumption, while negative values indicate token credit","AGGREGATION":"Aggregation","ALL":"All","ALL_AVAILABLE_DATA":"All available data","ALL_DATA":"All data","ALL_DATES":"All dates","ALL_EXPORT_ONBOARDING_TOOLTIP_HEADER":"Export account data","ALL_EXPORT_ONBOARDING_TOOLTIP_SUBTEXT":"Download user, subscription, and usage data to help you analyze and share information.","ALL_EXPORT_SUBTITLE":"Downloading data helps you analyze, maintain, and share account information in spreadsheet format.","ALL_ITEMS_SELECTED":"All items selected","ALL_PRODUCTS":"All products","ALL_TEAMS":"All Teams","AND":"and","ANNUAL_MULTI_YEAR":"annual or multi-year","APPLY":"Apply","ASSIGNED":"Assigned","ASSIGNED_AND_UNASSIGNED":"Assigned and unassigned","ASSIGNED_SEATS":"Assigned seats","ASSIGNED_SEATS_ONBOARDING_HEADER":"Seat assignments at a glance","ASSIGNED_SEATS_ONBOARDING_MESSAGE":"Track assignments to help you optimize use and get the most out of your subscription. See product-specific seat assignments on the By product tab.","ASSIGNED_SEATS_WITH_COUNT":"Assigned seats ({{count}})","ASSIGN_USERS":"Assign users","ASSIGNMENTS":"Assignments","AVAILABLE":"Available","AVAILABLE_SEATS":"Available seats","AVERAGE_FREQUENCY":"Average frequency","AVERAGE_TOKEND_USED":"average tokens used","AVERAGE_TOKENS_MONTH":"Average tokens used each month","AVERAGE_USE":"Average use","BACK_TO_CATEGORIES":"Back to categories","BAR_LABEL":"{{ available | int }} of {{ total | int }} seats available","BETA_FOOTER_TEXT":"Beta Version. Autodesk makes no commitments with respect to beta versions regarding any features, functions, service levels or data and provides no warranties of any kind with respect to beta versions. Autodesk may choose not to generally release any beta versions or convert any beta version into a product offering.