 enough time has passed to generate meaningful insights or you have selected a team that has no insights available.","NO_INSIGHTS_AVAILABLE":"No insights available","NO_INSIGHTS_DESCRIPTION_INPRODUCT":"There are several reasons why insights might not be available for you.","NO_INSIGHTS_HEADER":"No insights available","NO_INSIGHTS_LINK_TEXT_INPRODUCT":"Why am I not getting insights?","NO_INSIGHTS_MESSAGE":"This occurs because no insights are generated.","NO_USAGE_MSG":"No usage for the selected date range","OCCASIONAL":"Occasional","OF":"of","OF_FRACTIONAL":"{{ numerator }} of {{ denominator }}","OFF":"OFF","OLDER":"Older","OLDER_VERSIONS":"Older versions","ON":"ON","ONE_PRODUCT_NOT_UNASSIGNED":"1 product not unassigned.","ONE_PRODUCT_SELECTED":"1 product selected","ONE_PRODUCT_STILL_ASSIGNED":"1 product is still assigned","ONBOARDING_INACTIVE_CONTENT":"If a user doesn’t access an assigned product in at least 3 months, they are considered inactive. Inactive user reporting helps you identify seats you might reassign to maximize the value of your subscription. Go to By User details to view individual activity or Insights to see all inactive users.","ONBOARDING_INACTIVE_HEADER":"View user inactivity and last access dates","OPTIMIZE_YOUR_SUBSCRIPTION":"Optimize your subscriptions with insights","OTHER_PRODUCTS_AND_COLLECTION":"Other products and collections","OUTLIER_VERSIONS_MSG":"Outlier versions account for less than 1% of a product\'s total use in the past 3 months.","OVERASSIGNED_SEATS":"Over-assigned seats","OVER_ASSIGNED":"over-assigned","OVER_ASSIGNED_DESC":"Over assignment occurs when one or more of your subscription seats has expired or were not renewed.","OVER_ASSIGNED_NOTE":"Note: Purchased seats may take up to 24 hours to reflect in insights.","OVER_ASSIGNED_PRODUCT":"over-assigned product","OVER_ASSIGNED_PRODUCTS":"over-assigned products","OVER_ASSIGNED_WARNING":"Note: It can take up to 24 hours to include newly purchased seats in insights.","OVER_ASSIGNMEN