artup and the time it takes to open and save files. Optimizing performance can help.","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_DETAILS_MSG":"Users who experienced slower than benchmark Startup, File Open or File save times based on usage. [What is the benchmark?]","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_DETAILS_MSGII":"Consider checking in with users to diagnose any product performance issues, commonly caused by an outdated machine or product.","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_DETAILS_SUBTITLE":"Users who are experiencing slower than benchmark product performance compared to the all user average","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SEE_ALL":"See all product performance","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SEE_ALL_TEAMS":"See all teams","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SUMMARY_DESCRIPTION":"Team with the lowest product performance","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SUMMARY_DESCRIPTION_SINGULAR":"user with slow product performance","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SUMMARY_DESCRIPTION_PLURAL":"users with slow product performance","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SUMMARY_NOTE":"These insights do not include users who didn\'t use the product in the stated time period.","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SUMMARY_TITLE":"Performance is compared to all AutoCAD users assigned to a team and using a supported version in the past 30 days.","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_SYSTEM_REQUIREMENTS":"System requirements","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_TITLE_SINGULAR":"user experienced slower than benchmark Startup, File Open or File save times in the past 30 days for AutoCAD.","PRODUCT_PERFORMANCE_TITLE_PLURAL":"users experienced slower than benchmark Startup, File Open or File save times in the past 30 days for AutoCAD.","PRODUCTS":"Products","PRODUCTS_COUNT":"Products ({{count}})","PRODUCTS_IN_USE":"Products in use","PRODUCTS_NOT_UNASSIGNED":"{{count}} products not unassigned.","PRODUCTS_STILL_ASSIGNED":"{{count}} products are still assigned","PRODUCTS_UNASSIGNED_WARNING":"{{count}} of {{totalCount}} products unassigned.","PRODUCTS_USED":"Products used","PRODUCTS_USED_BY_DAY":"Products used by day","PRODUCTS_WITH_INACTIVE_USERS":"Products with i