ing report","REMAINING_TOKEN_BALANCE":"Remaining balance of {{tokens}} tokens moved","RESET":"Reset","RESULTS_COUNT":"{{count}} results","RETRY":"Retry","SAVE":"Save","SCHEDULE_SAVE_MESSAGE":"Schedule saved successfully","SEATS":"Seats","SEATS_AVAILABLE":"{{available_seats}} of {{total_seats}} seats available","SEAT_ASSIGNMENTS":"Seat assignments","SEAT_USAGE":"Seat Usage","SEAT_USAGE_DESC":"Reporting for subscriptions with single user access","SEAT_USAGE_DESC_v2":"Reporting for subscriptions with single-user access","SEE_ALL_INACTIVE_USERS":"see all inactive users","SEE_ALL_PRODUCTS":"See all products","SEE_MY_INSIGHTS":"See all of my insights","SEE_OVER_ASSIGNED":"See all over-assigned","SEE_TEAM_INSIGHTS":"See all team insights","SEE_UNDER_ASSIGNED":"See all under-assigned","SELECTED":"selected","SELECTED_COUNT":"{{count}} selected","SELECT_A_CATEGORY":"Select a category to view your top commands.","SELECT_A_TEAM":"Select a team","SELECT_A_TEAM_DESC":"Select a team to view any inactive users for the last 3, 6, 9 or 12 months.","SELECT_CUSTOM_DATE":"Select a custom date","SELECT_DATE_RANGE":"Select date range","SERIAL_NUMBER_BANNER":"Seat usage will not report on serial number licenses after March 23, 2021. In most cases, this affects data for 2016 and older product versions. If you are tracking usage for these products, please export your data before this date.","SERVER_NAME":"Server name","SESSION":"Session","SESSION_DETAILS":"Session details","SESSION_DETAILS_BETA":"Session Details - Beta","SETTINGS_HEADER":"Select a team to edit settings. Settings do not apply across teams.","SET_COMMUNICATION":"Set your communication preferences","SET_GRID":"Set grid and snap, polar and object snap tracking, object snap modes, Dynamic Input and QP.","SHOW_LESS":"Show less","SHOW_MORE":"Show more","SMALL_SCREEN_ALERT_INFO":"More details are available when viewed on a larger screen.","SMALL_SCREEN_DAYS_SUBTITLE":"Past {{numDays}} days","STATUS":"Status","START_DATE":"Start Date