u use. Explore the benefits in Insights or Home.","TEAM_INSIGHTS":"Team insights","TEAM_INSIGHTS_EXPORT_DRILL_IN_TOOLTIP_MESSAGE":"Downloading detailed data helps you analyze and share insights in spreadsheet format. User-level data is only available for Premium plans.","TEAM_INSIGHTS_HELP_INFO":"Team insights help inform administrative tasks to better organize teams. User-level details only available for Premium plans, {{1}} learn more {{1}}. Filter by teams or categories to consider what actions to take.","TEAM_INSIGHTS_VIEW_TOOLTIP_MESSAGE":"View insights across all your teams and export data to analyze and manage team activity.","TEAM_SETTINGS":"Team settings","TFLEX_DATA_UNAVAILABLE_HEADER":"Token Flex usage data is not included in this report.","TFLEX_DATA_UNAVAILABLE_LINK":"Go to Token Flex reporting to export.","TFLEX_EXPORT_DISCLAIMER":"For your convenience, Autodesk offers functions that let you review your and/or your personnel\'s Autodesk services usage information. By accessing this information, you acknowledge and agree that you have taken responsibility for any notice and consent requirements under local data privacy and employment laws. For more information see the","TFLEX_MODAL_BY_USER_TOOLTIP":"View tokens used by product at a user level. Details include days used by version.","TFLEX_MODAL_ONBOARDING_MESSAGE":"Token Usage By User summarizes tokens used by product to help you track use and estimate tokens needed.","TFLEX_MODAL_ONBOARDING_TITLE":"Monitor Flex token use with user level data","TFLEX_UNAVAILABLE_SUMMARY":"Only primary and secondary admins can view token usage summary.","TFLEX_UNAVAILABLE_ADJUSTMENTS":"Only primary and secondary admins can view token adjustments.","TFLEX_UNAVAILABLE_DESKTOP_USAGE":"Only primary and secondary admins can view desktop product usage.","TFLEX_UNAVAILABLE_CLOUD_USAGE":"Only primary and secondary admins can view cloud product usage.","THIS_MONTH":"This month","TIME_USED":"Time used","TIME_USED_TOOLTIP":"The amo