_FILE":"Can\'t find the file?","HOW_DO_I_FIND_FILE":"How do I find the file","BROWSE_FILE_FROM_YOUR_COMPUTER_INSTEAD":"Browse file from your computer instead.","IDENTITY_PROVIDER":"Identity provider","ENTITY_ID":"Entity ID","PASSES_AUTHORIZATION_CREDENTIALS_TO_AUTODESK":"Passes authorization credentials to Autodesk.","SIGN_ON_URL":"Sign-on URL","REDIRECTS_USER_TO_YOUR_IDENTITY_PROVIDER":"Redirects users to your identity provider.","BINDING_METHOD":"Binding method","BINDING_METHOD_TOOLTIP_TEXT":"Binding is a method used to transport the authentication requests and responses sent between Autodesk and your identity provider.","CERTIFICATE_EXPIRED_LINK":"upload a renewed certificate.","POSE":"Pose","REDIRECT":"Redirect","POST":"Post","UPLOAD":"Upload","IN":"in","APPEARS_AS":"Appears as","USES_ONE_SET_OF_CREDENTIALS":"Uses one set of credentials to log into many diffeyarn urent sites.","IDP_CERTIFICATE":"Identity provider certificate","CERTIFICATE_EXPIRED":"If your certificate expired,","UPLOAD_CERTIFICATE":"upload a renewed certificate","UPLOAD_THE_CERTIFICATE":"Upload the certificate","OR_COPY_IT":"or copy it into the field.","FULL_URL_ERROR_MSG":"Please provide the full URL including http:// or https:// from your identity provider","CANCEL_SSO_CONNECTION_SETUP":"Cancel SSO connection setup","SETUP_INFORMATION_WILL_NOT_BE_SAVED":"Setup information will not be saved.","SETUP_CONNECTION_CLOSE_WARNING_MSG":"Connection name and identity provider metadata information will be saved. You can enter additional setup information later.","HERE":"here","DOWNLOAD":"Download","MAP_ATTRIBUTES":"Map attributes","ACS_URL":"Assertion Customer Service (ACS) URL","VERIFICATION_CERTIFICATE":"Verification certificate","EXAMPLE":"Example","IDENTITY_PROVIDER_TAKES_EFFECT_IMMEDIATELY":"Identity provider takes effect immediately","CURRENT_AUTODESK_ACCOUNTS_REGISTERED":"Current Autodesk accounts registered with domain.com email address will be immediately switched to signing in through your identity provider.","PLEASE_ENSURE_YOUR_USERS_ARE":"Please ensure your users are well-communicated about the change.","MY_SIGN_IN_METHOD_MAY_BE_IMPACTED":"My sign in method may be impacted","WHEN_THE_CONNECTION_IS_ENABLED":"When the connection is enabled, my account may be impacted by the change and I may require to sign in through my identity provider going forward.","CONFIRM_GO_LIVE":"Confirm go live","DOMAIN":"Domain","UPLOAD_AN_HTML_FILE_MSG":"Upload an HTML file to your website root directory for immediate verification or add a new TXT record to your domain name system (DNS). DNS verification can take up to 72 hours.","UPLOAD_HTML_FILE":"Upload HTML file","CREATE_DNS_TXT_RECORD":"Create DNS TXT record","DOWNLOAD_THE":"Download the","HTML_VERIFICATION_FILE":"HTML verification file","UPLOAD_THE_FILE_TO_ROOT_DIRECTORY":"Upload the file to the root directory of {{domainName}}. Do not rename this file or remove it after verifying your domain.","CONFIRM_THE_FILE_WAS_UPLOADED":"Confirm the file was uploaded by visiting:","COPY_THIS_INFORMATION_DNS_TXT":"Copy this information and paste it into a new TXT record in your domain name system (DNS) server. Verification can take up to 72 hours.","ALIAS_OR_HOST_NAME":"Alias or host name","DESTINATION_OR_POINTS_TO_ADDRESS":"Destination or points to address","TTL":"TTL","COPY":"Copy","COPIED":"Copied","HAVING_TROUBLE_VERIFYING_YOUR_DOMAIN":"Having trouble verifying your domain?","TROUBLESHOOT":"Troubleshoot","URL":"URL","VERIFIED":"Verified","NOT_VERIFIED":"Not verified","LINKED":"Already linked","NOT_LINKED":"Not linked","DELETE":"Delete","DELETE_DOMAIN_CONFIRMATION":"After deleting this domain from {{teamName}}, it will be available for other teams to verify or you can add it back to this team later.","DELETE_DOMAIN":"Delete domain","ADD_DOMAINS":"Add domains","ADD_INDIVIDUAL":"Add individual","IMPORT_MULTIPLE":"Import multiple","YOU_CAN_ASSOCIATE_A_DOMAIN":"You can associate a domain with only one team. Add one or more domains for {{teamName}}. If adding more than 10 domains, consider importing a CSV file.","YOUR_EMAIL_DOMAIN":"Your email domain","EXAMPLE_DOMAIN":"Example: organizationdomain.com","ADD":"Add","REMOVE":"Remove","DOMAIN_LIMIT_MESSAGE":"You can add {{count}} individual domains at a time. If you need to add more than {{count}}, consider importing your domains from a CSV file.","INVALID_DOMAIN_ERR":"Enter a valid email domain. Example: organizationdomain.com","INVALID_DOMAIN_ERR_CSV":"Enter a valid email domain to successfully import your CSV file. Example: organizationdomain.com.","DOMAIN_ALREADY_IN_USE_ERR":"This domain is already in use by your team.","DOMAIN_ALREADY_IN_USE_ERR_CSV":"Domain is already added to this team. Delete this domain to successfully import your CSV file.","DOMAIN_LIMIT_EXCEEDED_ERROR":"You can add up to {{count}} domains. If you need to add more, check to see if you have unverified domains that you can delete.","DOMAIN_IS_NOT_AVAILBLE_FOR_TEAM":"This domain is no longer available for this team because it was verified by another team.","CSV_DOMAIN_LIMIT":"You can add up to 1,000 domains. Existing domains won\'t be imported.","CSV_FILE_INFO":"Upload a comma-separated values(CSV) file, listing the domains to import as shown in the table.","MULTIPLE_DOMAINS_CSV_INFO":"Enter “Email domain” in row 1 as shown in the example, then add your email domains starting on row 2.","IMPORT_CSV_TITLE":"Import information","UPLOAD_A_CSV_BUTTON_TITLE":"Upload CSV file","ADDING_DOMAINS":"Adding domains","NETWORK_ERROR_MSG":"It looks like you aren\'t connected to the internet or the service isn\'t available.","UNABLE_TO_VERIFY":"Unable to verify","CONFIRM_FILE_WAS_UPLOADED":"Confirm that the file was uploaded correctly to your root directory.","CONFIRM_DNS_TXT_ADDED":"Confirm that a TXT record with the necessary information was added to your DNS server.","DOMAIN_VERIFIED_SUCCESS_MSG":"verified. Click Manage SSO to continue setup.","PREV":"Prev","UNABLE_TO_LOAD_DOMAINS":"Unable to access domains","UNABLE_TO_ACCESS_SSO_SETUP":"Unable to access SSO setup","PERMISSIONS_ERROR_TEXT":"It looks like you don\'t have access to manage single sign-on. Contact your admin to request access.","REFRESH":"Refresh","DELETE_DOMAIN_ERROR":"An unknown error occurred. Try deleting the domain again. If the problem continues, contact support.","DELETE_INVALID_DOMAIN_ERROR_MSG":"This domain appears to be deleted. Close to update the Domains list.","SELECT":"Select","VERIFY_DOMAIN_ERROR":"An unknown error occurred. Try verifying the domains again. If the problem continues, contact support.","ADD_METADATA_HEADER_TXT":"This metadata allows your identity provider to communicate back to Autodesk for user authentication.","ADD_METADATA":"Add metadata","ADD_METADATA_HELPER_TXT":"For automatic setup, download the Autodesk metadata file and upload it to your identity provider. If you can\'t upload the file, select Manual Setup to add the information yourself.","DOWNLOAD_METADATA_FILE_AND_UPLOAD":"Download the Autodesk metadata XML file and upload to your identity provider.","COPY_THIS_INFO_AND_PASTE":"Copy this information and paste it into the corresponding fields in your identity provider.","IDENTITY_ID_TOOLTIP_TEXT":"Your identity provider uses this ID to identify Autodesk.","SIGN_ON_URL_TOOLTIP_TEXT":"We use this URL to redirect users to sign in with SSO.","ACS_URL_TOOLTIP_TEXT":"Your identity provider uses this URL to send its response after authenticating a user. We verify the response and redirect users using the sign-on URL.","VERIFICATION_CERT_TOOLTIP_TEXT":"Your identity provider uses this certificate to verify authentication requests from Autodesk.","IDENTITY_PROVIDER_USER_INFORMATION":"Identity provider user information","AUTODESK_ATTRIBUTE_NAMES":"Autodesk attribute names","IDENTITY_PROVIDER_USER_INFO_TEXT":"Identity provider user information must be mapped to the Autodesk attribute names, which are case-sensitive and contain no spaces. If they don\'t match